          "text": "USP_GetProjectChangeDetailsByScenarioId",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve aggregated project change details based on a specific scenario ID. It queries data from a view "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "vwProjectChangeDetailsMonthly",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " and joins it with the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Scenario",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table to filter results by the provided scenario ID. The procedure aggregates various usage metrics and groups the results by project change ID, agency code, budget group ID, and billing period."
        }
      ]
